overview: Jillian Michaels Kickbox FastFix is a total body workout that will fix your physique fast!! These quick-paced workouts will blast off the fat while toning your entire body.  Never kickboxed before?  Don't worry!  This tutorial helps you get familiar with the moves so you can perfect your form before you begin exercising.
title: Jillian Michaels Kickbox FastFix - Tutorial
